Based,in,Kenya,Lipisha,offers,a,payment,platform,for,businesses,that,enables,them,to,collect,process,and,integrate,payments,from,customers,and,clients,using,mobile,money,such,as,M,Pesa,or,Airtel,Money,The,Lipisha,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,with,the,Lipisha,payments,system,The,API,carries,out,a,number,of,activities,including,creating,a,new,payment,account,querying,for,transactions,Sending,mobile,money,charge,a,credit,or,debit,card,transferring,funds,between,different,Lipisha,accounts,and,more